name: BR Crafts
overview:
Established in the year 2000, we at BR Crafts, are engaged in Manufacturing and Exporting the most sought after range of Furniture, Architectural Works, Hand Crafted Gift Items, Home Decorations and Lifestyle Accessories.

Our Collection: Antique Wooden Bed, Wooden Single Bed, Royal Wooden Bed, Wooden Door, Wooden Railing, Wooden Arch, Wooden Temple Door, Wooden Entrance Door, Decorative Wooden Candle Stands, Unique Wooden Candle Stands, Printed Wooden Tieback, Designer Wooden Tieback, Round Wooden Tieback, White Wooden Wall Decor.

Infrastructure: Our company is able to cater to the ever rising demand for qualitative Power Conditioning Equipment with the state-of-the-art infrastructure facility. It is fully furnished with some of the latest and high-end tools and machinery Furniture, Architectural Works, Hand Crafted Gift Items, Home Decorations And Lifestyle Accessories.

Our Quality Assurance: Being a client centric organization, it is our constant endeavor to offer only flawless range of Furniture, Architectural Works, Hand Crafted Gift Items, Home Decorations And Lifestyle Accessories.

Client Satisfaction: The main goal of our company is to understand the diverse application requirements of our clients and offer suitable range of Furniture, Architectural Works, Hand Crafted Gift Items, Home Decorations and Lifestyle Accessories.
